          "activation_name": "Flames of Phlegethon",
          "effect": "You strike the ground with your axe, tearing open a one-way rift to the fourth layer of Hell in a 30-foot line that spews a curtain of hellfire. All creatures in the area take 6d6 fire damage and 6d6 spirit damage (DC 37 basic Reflex save) before the rift vanishes.",
